---
---
<section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
  <img
    class="hero-bg"
    src="/images/hero-meadow.webp"
    alt="A native meadow in golden afternoon light"
    width="2400"
    height="1600"
    fetchpriority="high"
    loading="eager"
  />
  <div class="hero-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="hero-content container">
    <p class="hero-label">A DOCUMENTARY FILM &middot; 2026</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title" id="hero-title">A Documentary Short About the American Yard</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Over 40 million acres of American lawn &ndash; roughly twice as much as every cotton field,
      rice paddy, potato crop, and fruit, nut, and berry orchard in the country combined. This is the story of the
      Americans who turned it back into something alive.
    </p>
    <a href="#founding-partner" class="btn btn-primary btn-hero">
      Join the Coalition
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100svh;
    min-height: 100vh; /* fallback */
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    /* Placeholder gradient — replaced when real photography is swapped in */
    background: linear-gradient(
      160deg,
      #0f1f0f 0%,
      #1e3a1e 30%,
      #2d4f2d 55%,
      #3a6335 80%,
      #2a4a28 100%
    );
  }

  @keyframes slow-zoom {
    from { transform: scale(1.06); }
    to   { transform: scale(1); }
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .hero-bg {
      animation: slow-zoom 8000ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) both;
    }
  }

  /* Semi-transparent overlay ensures text contrast against any photo */
  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(10, 25, 12, 0.72);
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: var(--space-24);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-24);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--color-amber);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #F7F3EC;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    max-width: 16ch;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #F7F3EC;
    max-width: 52ch;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    opacity: 1;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
  }

  .btn-hero {
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-12);
    min-height: 52px;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
    }

    .btn-hero {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 320px;
    }
  }
</style>
